    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone looking for a functional daily driver. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some paint fading on the hood, and a few small dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows clear signs of wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car is sound and starts up reliably, though it may require more frequent maintenance than a newer model. It\u2019s a solid, budget-friendly choice for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
