    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a few minor dings, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery and some fading on the dashboard plastics. Mechanically, the car starts and runs consistently, though it may soon require routine maintenance like new brake pads or a tire rotation. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at an affordable price point, provided they don't mind a few cosmetic imperfections.",
