    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished example of automotive excellence. This vehicle has been maintained to exacting standards, ensuring both mechanical integrity and a sophisticated aesthetic. Ideal for the discerning driver who values performance and reliability, it offers a seamless driving experience and a well-appointed interior. We invite you to experience the quality and refinement of this exceptional offering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
