      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Boasting a robust mechanical profile and a well-preserved interior, this model exemplifies the ideal balance of performance and long-term value. Our rigorous inspection process ensures that all vital systems operate at optimal levels, offering you a sophisticated driving experience with complete peace of mind. Secure an asset that delivers both prestige and reliability.",
      "price": 34900.0,
